Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:11.24,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:16.33,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:22.42,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I... to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.17,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...might love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:20.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Underground {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Secret Document
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:20.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Underground {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Secret Document
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:41.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:41.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Magic Academy's Crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Declaration of war"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sign the document.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cabinet has unanimously agreed to declare war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ally, Germania, has already agreed to join us and is waiting for you to make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, preparations to march into Albion are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Masarini, do you want to go to war that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand your love for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, most of the citizens are seeking military action against Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep postponing the war, a coup d'etat shall take place!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup d'etat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case, you would be put in jail,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the authority of the royal family would plummet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that were to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't want to start a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If an aggressive ruler were to come into power,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the war would only escalate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be nobody to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your presence, we can limit the bloodshed to bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I infer that your heart must be in turmoil,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Masarini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Poitier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Henrietta, as the Queen of Tristain, declare war upon Albion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our forces took the victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise Tristain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise our Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, it looks like we won the first battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The war broke out a week ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A large fleet of five hundred ships,\Nconsisting of Tristain and Germanian forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clashed with enemy troops before entering Albion territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and inflicted upon them devastating damage."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Damage to our side was minimal."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tristain's winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the Princess against the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's {\i1}Albion{\i0} that we're facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had no choice but to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Princess had to make a painful decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mister, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are sailor's clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fabric's pretty tough, and{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sailor uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Louise wear this, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be as great if Louise wore this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the Queen's permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Top secret document vault"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Beneath this academy, there is a vault for top secret documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received the privilege to access these documents from the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Principal Osmond said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he never received an order to undo the Lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and thus refused to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the Princess gave you the privilege?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was built over a thousand years ago, so there are handfuls of mystery within.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also heard that a spell was cast on it as a security measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entering carelessly will cost you your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not fear danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, what's this document you want to see so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has to do with my foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since our comrade is in trouble, I want to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I also called you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I may be better described as buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you can use special kinds of magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can dispel any kind of Lock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to use Unlock with Void magic, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't do it without concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, explosions seem to be the only kind of magic Louise can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She uses it like it's her only trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboom here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kaboom there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't possibly do something complicated like unlocking a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no better tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening Locks, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Saito-san thinking of doing, making me wear clothes like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Saito-san will like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he going into women's restroom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better to burn the documents instead of hiding them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once documents become official, they cannot be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be troublesome for others to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Government policies don't make sense now, nor did they a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three locks are used.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one is simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they can't be unlocked without the combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you figured out the combination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The binding of the Lock... undo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on alone from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets interesting from here on, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I unlocked the door because I'm curious to see what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might find records of magical experiments that were conducted in secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's dangerous, that's more reason not to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-kun. I though that the Principal was against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not take orders from cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Agnes-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Agnes said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When our forces take over Albion's port, the Queen will head to the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I will go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take care of this case before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess is going to the front line?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she couldn't sit by in a safe place,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having ordered hundreds of thousands of troops to go risk their lives fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who is your foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried on the clothes you gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought Saito-san was alone, but he had company with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Saito bought in town, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that from my uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that in Saito-san's home town, all young girls wear clothes like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you came from a distant country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was very nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he gave it to me saying, "I'm sure it'll look good on you, Siesta."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It wouldn't look good on Louise since she's got no breasts."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. I d-don't have any b-breasts, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're flat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're {\i1}concave{\i0}, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Miss Vallière, not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chibi-Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to consider the time and place when you use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even learned these basic rules yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I've mentioned them numerous times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about this unless there is an Earth mage nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we can't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting here and crying won't do us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your home town, do young girls go to war as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, isn't that a military uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my country, it's a school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither guys nor girls go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to visit your country sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the sailor uniform catch your interest, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean. I'm jealous of a country without war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that war doesn't exist there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand having young people become victims of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the midst of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the teacher's job to teach students to fight for their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that because you don't know what war is really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you saw the wretchedness of the battlefield even once...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village in which I was born was razed by the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was more like a massacre than a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be from...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago, insinuating acts of treason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the government destroyed a newly-formed sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, that "treason" was nothing more than a hoax from Lishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They quelled a rebellion that never took place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then got promoted for their achievements and gained power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that, my family and friends were...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Innocent people were burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I alone was saved by someone who carried me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, your foe is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already killed Lishman with these hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those who actually assaulted the\Nvillage must still be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that record is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's getting bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of high school days,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though I never had good experiences like this while I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the explosion for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, take the rear guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.89,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold back for now, but you better look forward to tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what do you intend to do when you find out who your foes are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do after you kill your foes, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight for the Queen, and then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were able to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to waste your life for vengeance and war?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you, ah... ever fallen in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think there are more important things than battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! I don't have time to argue with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only a rumour, but I heard that Captain Agnes likes girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "I thought so"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, something's written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The alteration, destruction, or removal of documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the use of magic, is forbidden."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use any to begin with, so you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who fail to abide will encounter a catastrophe."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's just a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on par with Romalia's religious library.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really so much stuff that needs to be hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the document you wanted to see, Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a recent file within these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, could you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Agnes, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking about love and whatnot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what I have on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dungletale Case"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, plebeian! Don't touch stuff when you don't know what you're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just used magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. The security magic is taking effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, Onee-sama! Aren't you supposed to\Nconsider the time and place when you use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, let's get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Order."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To prevent the spread of the epidemic, burn all humans near Dungletale."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Epidemic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-kun, we need to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I haven't found the captain's name yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A special force was put together to deal with the epidemic, and the captain was{\fscx300}-{\r}"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The section with his name has been torn away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's name must be somewhere...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not letting us go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Saito and the others are still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, do you have any magic for flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can levitate, but only when I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must run through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can go there now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'll revert back to the way it was next time we come...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert, it looks like you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I've gained a new impression of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very brave in an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I simply got scared and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's head back to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Epidemic countermeasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Although they said it was rebellion, there wasn't really one,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the massacre was ordered to remedy the epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the troops who carried out the\Nmission didn't know the truth behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to forgive them if that's the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not saying that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's strange for the captain's name to be ripped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place exists for the sake of holding every\Ndocument working against that individual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone came before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the captain himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot that Chibi-Louise collapsed the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, we give you special permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go flirt with Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Louise, wrong direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way! You need to blow {\i1}that{\i0} way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, another explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rowdy school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, it's the animal chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all get along well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you for locking me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The academy's under attack, you understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Academy's Crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
